donbe <- donall %>%
  select(, , .) %>%
  group_by(, , .) %>%
  count(.) %>%
  ungroup() %>%
  left_join(perall, by = c("" = "", "" = "")) %>%
  select(, , ., ) %>%
  filter( %in% c("", "")) %>%
  group_by(, .) %>%
  count(.) %>%
  filter(n>1) %>%
  mutate( = ifelse(n >= 1 & n <= 2, "",
                       ifelse(n >= 3 & n <= 5, "", ""))) %>%
  rename( = n)

donba <- donall %>%
  select(, , .) %>%
  group_by(, , .) %>%
  count(.) %>%
  ungroup() %>%
  left_join(perall, by = c("" = "", "" = "")) %>%
  select(, ., ) %>%
  filter( %in% c("", "")) %>%
  group_by(, ., ) %>%
  count(.) %>%
  ungroup() %>%
  filter(. %in% donbe$.) %>%
  left_join(donbe, by = c(".", "" = "")) %>%
  mutate(value = ifelse( == "", n, 0))

don_var <- donall %>%
  left_join(perall %>% select(, , ), by = c("", "")) %>%
  left_join(donra %>% select(., , ),  by = c(".", "")) %>%
  filter( %in% c("", "")) %>%
  filter(! == "") %>% 
  group_by(, ., ) %>%
  mutate(sum_per = sum()) %>% 
  distinct(, ., , .keep_all = TRUE) %>%
  group_by(, .) %>%
  summarise(mean = mean(sum_per), sd = sd(sum_per), cv = sd(sum_per) / mean(sum_per)) %>%
  filter(cv >= 0.5)
don_var %>%
  left_join(donall, , by = c(".", "")) %>%
  group_by(., , ) %>%
  mutate( = sum()) %>%
  distinct(, ., , .keep_all = TRUE) %>%
  left_join(perall %>% select(, , ), by = c("", "")) %>%
  filter( %in% c("", "")) %>%
  mutate( = case_when( >= mean ~ "", TRUE ~ ""),
          = case_when( == "" ~ 1, TRUE ~ 0)) %>%
  group_by(., , ) %>% 
  mutate( = n()) %>%
  group_by(., , , ) %>%
  mutate( = sum()) %>%
  distinct(., , , , .keep_all = TRUE) %>%
  group_by(., , ) %>%
  mutate( = sum()) %>%
  distinct(., , , .keep_all = TRUE) %>% 
  mutate(result =  / ) %>%
  spread(, result, fill = 0) %>%
  group_by(., ) %>%
  summarise( = sum(),  = sum()) %>%
  ggplot() +
  aes(x = , y = , color = ) %>%
  geom_jitter(width=0.05,height=0.05) +
  ggtitle("") +
  theme(text = element_text(family = "PingFangTC-Medium"))

don_3 <- donall %>%
  group_by(, .) %>%
  count(, .) %>%
  group_by(.) %>%
  count(.) %>%
  filter(nn == 3)
don_kuo <- donall %>%
  filter(. %in% don_3$.) %>%
  left_join(perall %>% select(, , ), by = c("", "")) %>%
  mutate(value = case_when( == "" ~ 0, TRUE ~ 1)) %>%
  group_by(, .) %>%
  summarise(all = sum(value)) %>%
  group_by(.) %>%
  summarise(a = sum(all)) %>%
  filter(a == 0)

don_min <- donall %>%
  filter(. %in% don_3$.) %>%
  left_join(perall %>% select(, , ), by = c("", "")) %>%
  mutate(value = case_when( == "" ~ 1, TRUE ~ 0)) %>%
  group_by(, .) %>%
  summarise(all = sum(value)) %>%
  group_by(.) %>%
  summarise(a = sum(all)) %>%
  filter(a == 0)
donall %>%
  filter(. %in% c(don_kuo$., don_min$.)) %>%
  mutate(party = case_when(. %in% don_kuo$. ~ "kuo",
                           TRUE ~ "min")) %>%
  group_by(, party) %>%
  summarise(all = sum()) %>%
  ggplot() +
  aes(x = , y = all, fill = party) +
  geom_bar(stat = "identity", position = "dodge") +
  theme(text = element_text(family = "PingFangTC-Medium")) +
  scale_fill_manual(values=c("#3399CC", "#99CC33"))

donall %>% 
  filter(. %in% don_kuo$.) %>%
  group_by(.) %>%
  summarise(all = sum()) %>%
  arrange(desc(all)) %>%
